data.description: **HUGE PRICE REDUCTION**Discover this immaculate home boasting stunning mountain views from its corner lot location. The impressive curb appeal is accentuated by the prestigious Barbaro (3570 floor plan), featuring 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Inside the open concept layout & split floor plan create a welcoming ambiance, highlighted by grey plank tile flooring & upgraded carpet in the bedrooms. Neutral paint tones throughout add to the modern aesthetic. The kitchen is a chef's delight equipped with stainless steel appliances, a gas stove & granite countertops. A barn door adds privacy to the expansive master suite which includes a double sink primary bathroom & a large walk-in closet. Additional features include a water softener & newly installed ROI system for enhanced convenience. Outside, enjoy low-maintenance desert landscaping with a sizable artificial turf area, an extended patio, and breathtaking views. Nestled in Peralta Canyon, this home offers access to exciting amenities such as horseshoes, bean bag toss, an outdoor fire pit, pickleball courts, and bocce ball. Ample green space invites relaxation and leisurely strolls, while the nearby Peralta Trails Regional Park provides excellent opportunities for walking and hiking amidst natural beauty. Experience the best of Arizona living in this inviting community.
